column1: #dig start(15;10; Top left corner of central stairs) Plumbing for the waterfall system, meant to be overlayed on top of already-dug-out floors. Start at the Z-level below the waterfall plumbing floor and use Alt+R to repeat downwards. Each repetition will do 2 floors (to accommodate the screw pump tower in the lower right).\n\nOn the bottommost level, the screw pumps placed there require 2 floor tiles to sit on, so remove or refloor the 2 norhternmost channel designations on the bottom Z-level of your tower.
